---
title: Maple-Mustard Tofu with Caramelized Onions and Garlicky Green Beans
description: Sweet maple syrup and punchy mustard is always a winning combination—especially when paired with tofu. Caramelized onions add another layer of flavour to round out this delicious family-friendly meal!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tofu-a-la-moutarde-et-a-lerable-b702ef3b.jpg
